items.text: My absolute favourite pub in London, brilliant selection of US and UK microbrewery beers. Their food is pretty good and during lunchtime I'd recommend the eggs benedict. Amazing Scotch eggs!
Showcases an extensive beer menu courtesy of Master of Brews Adam Simmons, & a mouthwatering menu of British gastro pub-style dishes to round things off.
Right next to Tower Bridge, with a large range of ales on tap and over 50 different bottled beers
Great beers in particular, but the staff were lots of fun too - I love a place with personality
Try the Scotch Duck Egg on the snack menu - amazing!
